Can't understand such low ratings for this joint. I have had food from this place(mostly takeaway) umpteen number of times. Never had an issue. The veg food here tastes better than anything I have eaten in any north indian restaurant in hyderabad. All those fancy fine dining restaurants from the famous chain of restaurants in hyderabad with amazing ambience can't hold a candle to this place when it comes to sheer taste.¬† If not having non-veg from Paradise this is my fav place to go. The taste is simply outstanding and one can never go wrong. This is a no nonsense place and is frequented by families as well. Waiters will not speak english nor will they be in fancy uniform. If you have a problem with the ambience/service then better do a take away. Visit only if you are hungry.Having said all that I expect similar taste from all the copies of Santosh dhabas across hyderabad as they all follow same north indian dhaba format.And yes dhaba food is going to be oily, so its not for daily dining, for health conscious Subway is the place.
